videos.description: Clemson's Aamir Simms goes down low and gets off a no-look pass to Tevin Mack for the wide-open 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Simms' no-look pass to Mack results in triple) 2020/2/15

videos.headline: Simms' no-look pass to Mack results in triple

videos.description: Clyde Trapp intercepts the pass and finishes on the other end with an easy lay-in against Louisville.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Clemson's Trapp forces steal, gets an easy 2) 2020/2/15

videos.headline: Clemson's Trapp forces steal, gets an easy 2

videos.description: Bill Murray is in the building to support his son Luke who serves as an assistant coach for Louisville.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Bill Murray in enemy territory to support Louisville) 2020/2/15

videos.headline: Bill Murray in enemy territory to support Louisville

videos.description: John Newman III's one-handed jam sends the Clemson crowd into a frenzy.

videos.headline: Newman's dunk has Clemson fans in awe

videos.description: Fans rush the court to celebrate as Clemson earns the upset over No. 5 Louisville 77-62.
